# SIEM Alert Reporting

## Task Summary
Investigated a phishing email alert in the TryHackMe SIEM platform. Analyzed suspicious indicators, verified malicious activity using VirusTotal, and documented findings using the 5W method.

## Skills Learned
- SIEM Monitoring
- Phishing Analysis
- SOC Alert Investigation
- Incident Reporting
- VirusTotal Analysis

## Outcome
Successfully identified the alert as a True Positive and completed the investigation process in a simulated SOC environment.
